{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Rescue_of_Lynae",
  "title": "The Rescue of Lynae",
  "summary": "Darth Malign mounts an audacious raid to free his captured officer Captain Lynae Caiton from the New Republic Star Destroyer Reprisal over Coruscant. A battered shuttle full of Storm Commandos disguised as Corellian refugees -- with Malign and Admiral Danik Kreldin among them -- broadcasts a false distress call, is chased by the Imperial Broadsword as cover, and is tractored into the Reprisal's hangar. The Republic's pilots Kyrin Sh'vani and Kesander, and hangar crew Rook and Lianna, are caught off guard when the 'refugees' shed their robes and Malign ignites his lightsaber, plunging the bay into a brutal firefight. The commandos blow a turbolift to scale the security level, slaughtering marines and freeing Lynae, while exotic black droids pour from the shuttle to seize the hangar's tractor controls. Luke Skywalker arrives by crash-landing his X-Wing and duels Malign and Kreldin amid the carnage. With time running out and casualties mounting, Malign extracts the rescue team, hurls a crane arm at the marines, and escapes aboard the commandeered shuttle with Lynae -- as Luke halts the falling crane with the Force to save the survivors.",
